  "root_text": {
    "dhp306:0.1": "Khuddakanikāya ",
    "dhp306:0.2": "Dhammapada ",
    "dhp306:0.3": "Nirayavagga ",
    "dhp306:0.4": "Sundarīparibbājikāvatthu ",
    "dhp306:1": "Abhūtavādī nirayaṁ upeti, ",
    "dhp306:2": "Yo vāpi katvā na karomi cāha; ",
    "dhp306:3": "Ubhopi te pecca samā bhavanti, ",
    "dhp306:4": "Nihīnakammā manujā parattha. ",
    "dhp307:0": "Duccaritaphalapīḷitavatthu ",
    "dhp307:1": "Kāsāvakaṇṭhā bahavo, ",
    "dhp307:2": "pāpadhammā asaññatā; ",
    "dhp307:3": "Pāpā pāpehi kammehi, ",
    "dhp307:4": "nirayaṁ te upapajjare. ",
    "dhp308:0": "Vaggumudātīriyabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp308:1": "Seyyo ayoguḷo bhutto, ",
    "dhp308:2": "tatto aggisikhūpamo; ",
    "dhp308:3": "Yañce bhuñjeyya dussīlo, ",
    "dhp308:4": "raṭṭhapiṇḍamasaññato. ",
    "dhp309:0": "Khemakaseṭṭhiputtavatthu ",
    "dhp309:1": "Cattāri ṭhānāni naro pamatto, ",
    "dhp309:2": "Āpajjati paradārūpasevī; ",
    "dhp309:3": "Apuññalābhaṁ na nikāmaseyyaṁ, ",
    "dhp309:4": "Nindaṁ tatīyaṁ nirayaṁ catutthaṁ. ",
    "dhp310:1": "Apuññalābho ca gatī ca pāpikā, ",
    "dhp310:2": "Bhītassa bhītāya ratī ca thokikā; ",
    "dhp310:3": "Rājā ca daṇḍaṁ garukaṁ paṇeti, ",
    "dhp310:4": "Tasmā naro paradāraṁ na seve. ",
    "dhp311:0": "Dubbacabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp311:1": "Kuso yathā duggahito, ",
    "dhp311:2": "hatthamevānukantati; ",
    "dhp311:3": "Sāmaññaṁ dupparāmaṭṭhaṁ, ",
    "dhp311:4": "nirayāyupakaḍḍhati. ",
    "dhp312:1": "Yaṁ kiñci sithilaṁ kammaṁ, ",
    "dhp312:2": "saṅkiliṭṭhañca yaṁ vataṁ; ",
    "dhp312:3": "Saṅkassaraṁ brahmacariyaṁ, ",
    "dhp312:4": "na taṁ hoti mahapphalaṁ. ",
    "dhp313:1": "Kayirā ce kayirāthenaṁ, ",
    "dhp313:2": "daḷhamenaṁ parakkame; ",
    "dhp313:3": "Sithilo hi paribbājo, ",
    "dhp313:4": "bhiyyo ākirate rajaṁ. ",
    "dhp314:0": "Issāpakataitthivatthu ",
    "dhp314:1": "Akataṁ dukkaṭaṁ seyyo, ",
    "dhp314:2": "pacchā tappati dukkaṭaṁ; ",
    "dhp314:3": "Katañca sukataṁ seyyo, ",
    "dhp314:4": "yaṁ katvā nānutappati. ",
    "dhp315:0": "Sambahulabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp315:1": "Nagaraṁ yathā paccantaṁ, ",
    "dhp315:2": "guttaṁ santarabāhiraṁ; ",
    "dhp315:3": "Evaṁ gopetha attānaṁ, ",
    "dhp315:4": "khaṇo vo mā upaccagā; ",
    "dhp315:5": "Khaṇātītā hi socanti, ",
    "dhp315:6": "nirayamhi samappitā. ",
    "dhp316:0": "Nigaṇṭhavatthu ",
    "dhp316:1": "Alajjitāye lajjanti, ",
    "dhp316:2": "lajjitāye na lajjare; ",
    "dhp316:3": "Micchādiṭṭhisamādānā, ",
    "dhp316:4": "sattā gacchanti duggatiṁ. ",
    "dhp317:1": "Abhaye bhayadassino, ",
    "dhp317:2": "bhaye cābhayadassino; ",
    "dhp317:3": "Micchādiṭṭhisamādānā, ",
    "dhp317:4": "sattā gacchanti duggatiṁ. ",
    "dhp318:0": "Titthiyasāvakavatthu ",
    "dhp318:1": "Avajje vajjamatino, ",
    "dhp318:2": "vajje cāvajjadassino; ",
    "dhp318:3": "Micchādiṭṭhisamādānā, ",
    "dhp318:4": "sattā gacchanti duggatiṁ. ",
    "dhp319:1": "Vajjañca vajjato ñatvā, ",
    "dhp319:2": "avajjañca avajjato; ",
    "dhp319:3": "Sammādiṭṭhisamādānā, ",
    "dhp319:4": "sattā gacchanti suggatiṁ. ",
    "dhp319:5": "Nirayavaggo dvāvīsatimo. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "dhp306:0.1": "Minor Collection ",
    "dhp306:0.2": "Sayings of the Dhamma 306–319 ",
    "dhp306:0.3": "22. Hell ",
    "dhp306:1": "A liar goes to hell, ",
    "dhp306:2": "as does one who denies what they did. ",
    "dhp306:3": "Both are equal in the hereafter, ",
    "dhp306:4": "those men of base deeds. ",
    "dhp307:1": "Many who wear a scrap of ocher cloth ",
    "dhp307:2": "are unrestrained and wicked. ",
    "dhp307:3": "Being wicked, they are reborn in hell ",
    "dhp307:4": "due to their bad deeds. ",
    "dhp308:1": "It’d be better for the immoral and unrestrained ",
    "dhp308:2": "to eat an iron ball, ",
    "dhp308:3": "scorching, like a burning flame, ",
    "dhp308:4": "than to eat the nation’s alms. ",
    "dhp309:1": "Four things befall a heedless man ",
    "dhp309:2": "who sleeps with another’s wife: ",
    "dhp309:3": "wickedness, poor sleep, ",
    "dhp309:4": "ill-repute, and rebirth in hell. ",
    "dhp310:1": "He accrues wickedness and is reborn in a bad place, ",
    "dhp310:2": "all so a frightened couple <j>may snatch a moment’s pleasure, ",
    "dhp310:3": "for which rulers impose a heavy punishment. ",
    "dhp310:4": "That’s why a man should not <j>sleep with another’s wife. ",
    "dhp311:1": "When kusa grass is wrongly grasped ",
    "dhp311:2": "it only cuts the hand. ",
    "dhp311:3": "So too, the ascetic life, when wrongly taken, ",
    "dhp311:4": "drags you to hell. ",
    "dhp312:1": "Any lax act, ",
    "dhp312:2": "any corrupt observance, ",
    "dhp312:3": "or suspicious spiritual life, ",
    "dhp312:4": "is not very fruitful. ",
    "dhp313:1": "If one is to do what should be done, ",
    "dhp313:2": "one should staunchly strive. ",
    "dhp313:3": "For the life gone forth when laxly led ",
    "dhp313:4": "just stirs up dust all the more. ",
    "dhp314:1": "A bad deed is better left undone, ",
    "dhp314:2": "for it will plague you later on. ",
    "dhp314:3": "A good deed is better done, ",
    "dhp314:4": "one that does not plague you. ",
    "dhp315:1": "As a frontier city ",
    "dhp315:2": "is guarded inside and out, ",
    "dhp315:3": "so you should ward yourselves—",
    "dhp315:4": "don’t let the moment pass you by. ",
    "dhp315:5": "For if you miss your moment ",
    "dhp315:6": "you’ll grieve when sent to hell. ",
    "dhp316:1": "Unashamed of what is shameful, ",
    "dhp316:2": "ashamed of what is not shameful; ",
    "dhp316:3": "beings who uphold wrong view ",
    "dhp316:4": "go to a bad place. ",
    "dhp317:1": "Seeing danger where there is none, ",
    "dhp317:2": "and blind to the actual danger, ",
    "dhp317:3": "beings who uphold wrong view ",
    "dhp317:4": "go to a bad place. ",
    "dhp318:1": "Seeing fault where there is none, ",
    "dhp318:2": "and blind to the actual fault, ",
    "dhp318:3": "beings who uphold wrong view ",
    "dhp318:4": "go to a bad place. ",
    "dhp319:1": "Knowing a fault as a fault ",
    "dhp319:2": "and the faultless as faultless, ",
    "dhp319:3": "beings who uphold right view ",
    "dhp319:4": "go to a good place. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "dhp306:2": "vāpi → yo cāpi (bj, mr) | na karomi cāha → na karomīti cāha (bj, sya-all, pts1ed) ",
    "dhp313:1": "Kayirā ce kayirāthenaṁ → kayirañce kayirathenaṁ (sya-all); kayirā ce kayirā naṁ (mr) ",
    "dhp315:4": "khaṇo vo → khaṇo ve (pts1ed, pts2ed, mr) "
  },
